### Protection Bypass with vercel curl

Source: https://github.com/vercel/vercel/blob/main/packages/cli/src/commands/curl/README.md

Explicitly provide a protection bypass secret using the --protection-bypass flag. This secret is used to bypass Vercel Protection on the target deployment.

```bash
vercel curl /api/protected \
  --protection-bypass your-secret-key \
  -- --request GET
```

